'''Homestar''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located on [[Treasure Ship Row/Legends|Treasure Ship Row]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. Its unremarkable exterior hid an expansive interior, complete with dancers and a live band. [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]] [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] and [[Ylenic It'kla]] got into a scuffle with three [[Gotal/Legends|Gotals]] here while [[Mission to Corellia (Clone Wars)|searching]] for [[Ratri Tane]].

